metadata.description: Latent space walk of the visual culture of Mexico, trained by a dataset of three thousand images of Mexican handicrafts. The image synthesis shows the imaginary of textures , colors and forms of Mexico . The cosmic race belongs to the colonized, to miscegenation, to colors, to those who accept death. Here the permanence of the visual culture of Mexico in the web 3.0
